  "elementOrder": ["b-kicker", "b-intro", "b-card-1", "b-card-2", "b-card-3"],
  "definitions": {
    "b-kicker": {
      "type": "elementHeading",
      "level": 6,
      "text": "METHODOLOGY",
      "align": "left",
      "width": "hug",
      "height": "hug"
    },
    "b-intro": {
      "type": "elementBody",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Three variables were isolated and tested independently using controlled reading tasks with 48 participants across two sessions. Each task measured reading speed (wpm) and error rate on a comprehension quiz.",
      "align": "left",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "marginBottom": "0.5rem"
    },
    "b-card-1": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Variable A — Weight\n\nTested Regular (400), Medium (500), and Light (300) at identical size and line-height. The hypothesis was that lighter weights reduce legibility in low-light conditions despite being aesthetically preferred.\n\n**Result:** Significant at p<0.01 for ambient light below 50 lux.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "slideUp",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "b-card-2": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Variable B — Size\n\nBody text tested at 14px, 16px, 18px, and 20px at 1440px and 375px viewport widths. Size gains were significant up to 18px, with diminishing returns thereafter.\n\n**Result:** 16px adequate on desktop; 18px recommended for mobile contexts with glare.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "slideUp",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.08
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "b-card-3": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Variable C — Line Height\n\nLine-height ratios tested: 1.2, 1.4, 1.6, 1.8. Optimal varied by line length. Short lines (45–55 chars) benefited from tighter leading; long lines (75+ chars) required 1.6 to prevent tracking errors.\n\n**Result:** Line length × line-height interaction was the strongest predictor.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "slideUp",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.16
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "gridMode": {
    "mobile": "columns",
    "desktop": "grid"
  },
  "gridDebug": false,
